    </event>
    <event type="cultural" n="5">
        <desc xml:lang="en">Composed poetry about Imam al-Shafi'i's birth (505 AH) and death (623 AH) dates: 'ولد الإمام الشافعي الرافعي خمسا وخمسمئ فعي شالت نعامته ثلاثا بعد عشرين وستمئ أسائل فاسمع'</desc>
    </event>
    <event type="cultural" n="6">
        <desc xml:lang="en">Mastered several manual crafts</desc>
    </event>
    <event type="cultural" n="7" when-custom="0773" cert="high">
        <desc xml:lang="en">Stated that Timur's first emergence was in a year of 'ʿadhāb' (calamity), referring to the numerical value of the word (ʿayn = 70, dhāl = 700, alif = 1, bāʾ = 2, totaling 773 AH)</desc>
    </event>
    <event type="legacy" n="1">
        <desc xml:lang="en">His son squandered his books after his death</desc>
    </event>
    <note type="personalia" xml:lang="en">He was a good, pious, and self-restrained man</note>
